WEBVTT

07:45.140 --> 07:46.310 line:80%
In my grief,

07:46.330 --> 07:47.850 line:80%
I shall suspend court for 3 days

07:47.850 --> 07:49.140 line:80%
and wear plain robes to mourn.

07:49.140 --> 07:51.700 line:80%
The whole realm shall mourn deeply.

07:52.140 --> 07:54.530 line:80%
Yes, Your Majesty.
